description: Los Lobos Burritos is bringing authentic Northern Mexican burritos stateside to the streets of Washington D.C.! Choose from the Tinga (slow cooked shredded chicken in a chipotle tomato sauce), the Chile Verde (shredded beef sauteed in a green pepper salsa), the Chile Colorado (beef sauteed in a red pepper salsa), or the Rajas (grilled and peeled Anaheim peppers sauteed with onions and cheese).
name: Los Lobos Burritos
